    "On this basis, ProLINK (Wang K. et al., 2024) proposes a novel pre-training and hinting framework designed for low-resource inductive reasoning in arbitrary knowledge graph without additional training.",
    "At the same time, TAGREAL (Jiang P. et al., 2023) is able to automatically generate high-quality query hints and retrieve supporting information from large text corpora to detect knowledge in pre-trained language models (PLMs).",
